content:
Simple shortcode to include icons from SVG sprites outside of menus.
{{&lt; icon &#34;thumbs-up&#34; &gt;}} Example:
Result Usage {{&lt; icon &quot;thumbs-up&quot; &gt;}} {{&lt; icon &quot;thumbs-down&quot; &gt;}} {{&lt; icon &quot;laugh&quot; &gt;}} {{&lt; icon &quot;lemon&quot; &gt;}} {{&lt; icon &quot;moon&quot; &gt;}}
